{"tid":2067783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇文隆：沒有人可以阻礙警方前進","createTime":"2020-06-17T08:33:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T08:09:18.000Z","uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3f81582dda64be46c5288a2a2dc06fefb134536e","tid":2067783,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T08:33:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DxWkKFe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDxWkKFe.jpg&h=8593e921&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n籲警減慢推進 社工劉家棟阻差辦公罪成判囚一年 申保釋候上訴遭拒<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3eahxQN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3eahxQN&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXGwomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=1de85127\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3eahxQN</a><br />\n<br />\n署理主任裁判官指，「沒有人可以阻礙警方前進，就如沒有人可阻撓追捕劫匪一樣」，當時警方「以寡敵眾」，被告不但阻礙警方，更打亂了警方陣勢；而被告與另外兩名狀似社工的人要求警方慢下來，「等同要警方背棄職務、放棄職責」，是完全不合理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/inmediahknet/9310\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finmediahknet%2F9310&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXGwomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=1c5d3840\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/inmediahknet/9310</a>"},{"pid":"a7d59637ef6099a4402e38103c6364bdf21da1db","tid":2067783,"uid":57205,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T08:34:38.000Z","msg":"制裁list"},{"pid":"971d8aa539a114f4584df0c47f303d14a4848f82","tid":2067783,"uid":125168,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"a7d59637ef6099a4402e38103c6364bdf21da1db","tid":2067783,"uid":57205,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T08:34:38.000Z","msg":"制裁list"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T08:35:39.000Z","msg":"班狗官講嘢真係on9無極限"},{"pid":"c7be7a63e82ae822fc4b03364f926d133b3d442d","tid":2067783,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T08:37:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"